{"reponsecode":0,"reponsemessage":"","data":{"ispaid":1,"exhibit_id":"XMT_yyqcxx","exhibition_name":"展览一区","location":"369,559","name":"越窑青瓷香薰  ","size":"西晋 通高21cm","like":19,"share_url":"mob/exhibit/detail?exhibit_id=78","share_url2":"https://share.morview.com/#/share?id=XMT_yyqcxx","is_favorited":0,"_3d_url":"","description":"古人很早就已经懂得，香薰有消除疲劳、排解抑郁等功效。自古以来，香在中国的帝王宫廷和富贵人家的起居生活中，是一个不可缺少的组成部分。|大约在春秋时代，人们就已经有焚香这一习惯了。不过，在秦汉以前，中国还没有沉香之类的“专业香料”传入，当时焚烧的，是兰蕙一类的香草。到了汉武帝时期，岭南与中原的交流日渐增多，南方的一些小国会根据天子的喜好，来进奉一些贡品，当他们得知汉武帝崇尚道教后，纷纷贡献珍奇的香料，后来，香料也就传入中原，很少再有人焚烧香草了。","images":["content/fileroot/museum/xmt_museum/image/PuQlZF3Sr_s.webp","content/fileroot/museum/xmt_museum/image/z7lWy8alK_s.webp","content/fileroot/museum/xmt_museum/image/z7lWy8alK1_s.webp","content/fileroot/museum/xmt_museum/image/z7lWy8alK2_s.webp","content/fileroot/museum/xmt_museum/image/z7lWy8alK3_s.webp"],"audio":[{"audiotype":"mandarin","filename":"content/fileroot/museum/xmt_museum/audio/r2LaWjV5La.mp3"}],"video":{"videourl":"","img":""}}}